        "q3": "Do your products contain any additives or fillers?",
        "a3": "No. We use only whole bud flower and solventless concentrates. Our products are free from additives, cutting agents, and artificial flavoring. What you taste is pure, craft cannabis.",
        "q4": "Are Sundaze products federally legal?",
        "a4": "Yes. All Sundaze products are derived from hemp and contain less than 0.3% Δ9 THC by dry weight, making them compliant with the 2018 Farm Bill.",
        "q5": "Will Sundaze products show up on a drug test?",
        "a5": "While our products are federally legal, they may still result in a positive drug test due to the presence of cannabinoids. We advise caution if you are subject to drug testing in your workplace or for any other reason.",
